=== Directory Entry ===

==== Version 4361 <!-- Game: Petit Copter --> ====

File entry flags:
* READONLY  = 0x01
* HIDDEN    = 0x02
* SYSTEM    = 0x04
* DIRECTORY = 0x10
* ARCHIVE   = 0x20
* NORMAL = 0x80

=== File data blocks ===

